{"about_the_game":"<strong>Red Planet Rampage</strong> is a dieselpunk western-themed arena shooter where robots face off on Mars with wacky modular guns. Win gun parts in auctions and assemble a unique combination among <i>hundreds</i> of possible weapons!<br><br>The game is developed by volunteers at Hackerspace NTNU and is free and open source!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Lore</h2><br>The robots responsible for terraforming Mars have donned cowboy hats and started wreaking havoc with staged shootouts and competitions where they auction off rudimentary weapon parts assembled from scrap. Terraforming Inc. is still investigating the cause of this disturbance, but rumors point to a fateful upload of a western film.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717710/extras/enlarger.gif?t=1733870436\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Modular weapons with wildly different parts; over 500 different combinations<br></li><li> Auctions where players bid on these weapon parts<br></li><li> Splitscreen <i>and</i> online multiplayer<br></li><li> Fast-paced movement with rewarding tech</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717710/extras/tetherReworkedLarger.gif?t=1733870436\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Weapons</h2> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Reload by playing a rhythm minigame or shaking a soda can<br></li><li> Shoot bouncing cowboy hats<br></li><li> Mount a frying pan at the end of your gun as a makeshift shield<br></li><li> Slay your enemies in one hit with a rubber barrel that wiggles uncontrollably<br></li><li> and more!</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717710/extras/telescope2.gif?t=1733870436\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717710/extras/promo.gif?t=1733870436\" />","achieve